 it's not something you wanna use too much.

35
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,600
 If you're using important, that's a trouble.

36
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,920
 But don't worry about important right now.

37
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:09,920
 Just imagine cascading means the closer, the higher priority.

38
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:15,560
 Closer to the tag the statement of CSS is than the higher priority that it is.

